com.cloudera.oryx.als.serving.generation

Class Generation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cloudera.oryx.als.serving.generation.Generation

  • public final class Generation
extends Object
    Encapsulates a "generation" of output in the Oryx recommender implementation. This is essentially the output from one run of the Computation Layer. It includes the generated model data -- at heart, the factored X and Y matrices, but also things like the configured CandidateFilter, derived values, and the set of known item IDs for each user.
    Author:
    Sean Owen
    See Also:
    GenerationLoader
